{"id":1107,"date":"2018-08-01T18:21:02","date_gmt":"2018-08-01T22:21:02","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/staging.cegepsl.qc.ca\/?post_type=professeur&#038;p=1107"},"modified":"2023-06-12T12:04:52","modified_gmt":"2023-06-12T16:04:52","slug":"marie-josee-rosa","status":"publish","type":"professeur","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/equipe\/marie-josee-rosa\/","title":{"rendered":"Marie-Jos\u00e9e Rosa"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Multidisciplinaire, Marie-Jos\u00e9e a compl\u00e9t\u00e9 un baccalaur\u00e9at en communication, une ma\u00eetrise en \u00e9tudes cin\u00e9matographiques et, apr\u00e8s un terrain d\u2019\u00e9tudes au Japon, un doctorat en anthropologie.<\/p>\n<p>Elle s\u2019int\u00e9resse tout particuli\u00e8rement au cin\u00e9ma et \u00e0 la culture de l\u2019Asie de l\u2019Est. Depuis le d\u00e9but de sa carri\u00e8re en enseignement, elle a donn\u00e9 les cours suivants :<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Langage du cin\u00e9ma<\/li>\n<li>Histoire du cin\u00e9ma<\/li>\n<li>Techniques de l\u2019image<\/li>\n<li>\u00c9criture des m\u00e9dias<\/li>\n<li>Pratiques du cin\u00e9ma<\/li>\n<li>Milieu du cin\u00e9ma au Qu\u00e9bec<\/li>\n<li>Cin\u00e9ma et culture nationale<\/li>\n<li>Cin\u00e9ma et culture qu\u00e9b\u00e9coise.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1108,"template":"","categorie-equipe":[202],"departement-equipe":[],"specialite-equipe":[],"etiquette-interne":[],"class_list":["post-1107","professeur","type-professeur","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","categorie-equipe-personnel-enseignant"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/professeur\/1107","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/professeur"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/professeur"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-js